(24, 2, 'Hotel', 'updated', 15, 'App\\Models\\Hotel', '{\"changed\":[\"address\",\"description\",\"facility\",\"additional_info\",\"cover\",\"map\",\"latitude\",\"longitude\",\"cancellation_policy\",\"updated_at\"],\"before\":{\"address\":\"Jl. Pantai Batu Bolong No.99, Canggu, Kec. Kuta Utara, Kabupaten Badung, 80361\\t,Bali, Indonesia\",\"description\":\"<p>While the passage of time has wrought certain changes, the true essence of Bali remains the same and Ametis Villa is the place for you experience the very soul of this heavenly island.<\\/p><p>Located in Canggu, Ametis Villa is about 35 minutes from Kuta. This area maintains its cultural roots and is dotted with productive rice terraces that extend to a rugged stretch of coastline. Canggu is popular within surfing and expatriate circles, sought out for its laidback lifestyle qualities away from the crowds and concrete jungle of Seminyak.<\\/p><p>Ametis Villa is a luxury lifestyle villa with a home-style concept that will make you feel like you truly belong. During your stay, you will be assigned a personal butler, who excels in the singular ability to anticipate your every need, and to exceed your every expectation.<\\/p><p>Conceived, built and managed with integrity, Ametis Villa is respectful of Bali&#39;s unique cultural heritage, seeks to interact with the local community and shows sensitivity towards the immediate environment<\\/p>\",\"facility\":\"<p>- Cruising\\/Sailing\\/Scuba Diving\\/Snorkelling<br \\/>- Surfing<br \\/>- White Water Rafting<br \\/>- Golf and Tennis<br \\/>- Fishing<br \\/>- Horse Riding<br \\/>- Elephant Safari Park<br \\/>- Water Sports<br \\/>- Surfing and Body Boarding<br \\/>- Waterbom Park<br \\/>- Bali Bird Park Safari<br \\/>- Bali Safari &amp; Marine Park<br \\/>- RUBY SPA<br \\/>- Private Villa<\\/p>\",\"additional_info\":\"<p><strong>Standard benefit :<\\/strong><\\/p><p>Daily breakfast, Personal butler service, personalized villa check in&amp;out, 30Mins relaxing massage, daily sunset cocktail and canapes 18.00-20.00, daily afternoon tea 15.00-18.00, daily restocked minibar (soft drink, beer), daily restocked coffee, ea and homemade snack in villa, daily replenished fresh fruit in villa<\\/p><p>Add value for stay in Imperial Villa : upgrade 1x30mins into 60mins body massage at Ruby Spa, daily laundry up to 8 pieces\\/day\\/villa<\\/p><p><strong>Children policy :<\\/strong><\\/p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Accommodation at Ametis Villa is available only for guest aged 12 years and above<\\/p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Children aged between 12 years and 16 years old have alternative to stay with their parents in the same villa on existing sofa bed in Imperial Villa and Grand Villa<\\/p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Eternal home-style dining and Ametis Lounge is available for children under 12 years old who should be accompanied by parents or guardian.<\\/p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; In case Ametis Villa receives guest check-in with children under 12 years old without any advance notice, Ametis Villa has full authority to relocate guest to another hotel.<\\/p><p><strong>Honeymoon benefit :<\\/strong><\\/p><p>&bull; Honeymoon flower and cake upon arrival<\\/p><p>&bull; Departure gift<\\/p><p><strong>Seasonal policy :<\\/strong><\\/p><p>No Check-in nor Check-out is allowed on 31st December 2022<\\/p>\",\"cover\":\"1700187515_Ametis.webp\",\"map\":\"https:\\/\\/g.page\\/ametisvillabali?share\",\"latitude\":null,\"longitude\":null,\"cancellation_policy\":\"<p><strong>Regular Season:<\\/strong><\\/p><p>&bull; 14 days before arrival: one night cancellation fee per villa<\\/p><p>&bull; 7 days before arrival: full night&rsquo;s cancellation fee per villa<\\/p><p>&bull; No shows and early departures will be charged in full for the total number of nights per room reserved<\\/p><p><strong>High Season:<\\/strong><\\/p><p>&bull; 21 days before arrival: one night cancellation fee per villa<\\/p><p>&bull; 14 days before arrival: full night&rsquo;s cancellation fee per villa<\\/p><p>&bull; No shows and early departures will be charged in full for the total number of nights per room reserved<\\/p><p><strong>Peak Season:<\\/strong><\\/p><p>&bull; 30 days before arrival: one night cancellation fee per villa<\\/p><p>&bull; 21 days before arrival: full night&rsquo;s cancellation fee per villa<\\/p><p>&bull; No shows and early departures will be charged in full for the total number of nights per room reserved<\\/p>\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-25T02:26:55.000000Z\"},\"after\":{\"address\":\"Canggu, Bali, Indonesia\",\"description\":\"<p>While the passage of time has wrought certain changes, the true essence of Bali remains the same and Ametis Villa is the place for you experience the very soul of this heavenly island.<\\/p><p>Located in Canggu, Ametis Villa is about 35 minutes from Kuta. This area maintains its cultural roots and is dotted with productive rice terraces that extend to a rugged stretch of coastline. Canggu is popular within surfing and expatriate circles, sought out for its laidback lifestyle qualities away from the crowds and concrete jungle of Seminyak.<\\/p><p>Ametis Villa is a luxury lifestyle villa with a home-style concept that will make you feel like you truly belong. During your stay, you will be assigned a personal butler, who excels in the singular ability to anticipate your every need, and to exceed your every expectation.<\\/p><p>Conceived, built and managed with integrity, Ametis Villa is respectful of Bali\'s unique cultural heritage, seeks to interact with the local community and shows sensitivity towards the immediate environment<\\/p>\",\"facility\":\"<p>- Cruising\\/Sailing\\/Scuba Diving\\/Snorkelling<br>- Surfing<br>- White Water Rafting<br>- Golf and Tennis<br>- Fishing<br>- Horse Riding<br>- Elephant Safari Park<br>- Water Sports<br>- Surfing and Body Boarding<br>- Waterbom Park<br>- Bali Bird Park Safari<br>- Bali Safari &amp; Marine Park<br>- RUBY SPA<br>- Private Villa<\\/p>\",\"additional_info\":\"<p><strong>Standard benefit :<\\/strong><\\/p><p>Daily breakfast, Personal butler service, personalized villa check in&amp;out, 30Mins relaxing massage, daily sunset cocktail and canapes 18.00-20.00, daily afternoon tea 15.00-18.00, daily restocked minibar (soft drink, beer), daily restocked coffee, ea and homemade snack in villa, daily replenished fresh fruit in villa<\\/p><p>Add value for stay in Imperial Villa : upgrade 1x30mins into 60mins body massage at Ruby Spa, daily laundry up to 8 pieces\\/day\\/villa<\\/p><p><strong>Children policy :<\\/strong><\\/p><p>\\u00b7&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Accommodation at Ametis Villa is available only for guest aged 12 years and above<\\/p><p>\\u00b7&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Children aged between 12 years and 16 years old have alternative to stay with their parents in the same villa on existing sofa bed in Imperial Villa and Grand Villa<\\/p><p>\\u00b7&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Eternal home-style dining and Ametis Lounge is available for children under 12 years old who should be accompanied by parents or guardian.<\\/p><p>\\u00b7&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; In case Ametis Villa receives guest check-in with children under 12 years old without any advance notice, Ametis Villa has full authority to relocate guest to another hotel.<\\/p><p><strong>Honeymoon benefit :<\\/strong><\\/p><p>\\u2022 Honeymoon flower and cake upon arrival<\\/p><p>\\u2022 Departure gift<\\/p><p><strong>Seasonal policy :<\\/strong><\\/p><p>No Check-in nor Check-out is allowed on 31st December 2022<\\/p>\",\"cover\":\"hotels\\/covers\\/1700187515_Ametis.webp\",\"map\":\"https:\\/\\/www.google.com\\/maps\\/place\\/Ametis+Villa\\/@-8.6569645,115.1289464,17z\\/data=!4m10!3m9!1s0x2dd2387c49d72c23:0x963f451148ce5cbb!5m3!1s2026-03-25!4m1!1i2!8m2!3d-8.6569698!4d115.1315213!16s%2Fg%2F11xxm9hzj?entry=ttu&g_ep=EgoyMDI2MDMyMi4wIKXMDSoASAFQAw%3D%3D\",\"latitude\":\"-8.6568210\",\"longitude\":\"115.1315444\",\"cancellation_policy\":\"<p><strong>Regular Season:<\\/strong><\\/p><p>\\u2022 14 days before arrival: one night cancellation fee per villa<\\/p><p>\\u2022 7 days before arrival: full night\\u2019s cancellation fee per villa<\\/p><p>\\u2022 No shows and early departures will be charged in full for the total number of nights per room reserved<\\/p><p><strong>High Season:<\\/strong><\\/p><p>\\u2022 21 days before arrival: one night cancellation fee per villa<\\/p><p>\\u2022 14 days before arrival: full night\\u2019s cancellation fee per villa<\\/p><p>\\u2022 No shows and early departures will be charged in full for the total number of nights per room reserved<\\/p><p><strong>Peak Season:<\\/strong><\\/p><p>\\u2022 30 days before arrival: one night cancellation fee per villa<\\/p><p>\\u2022 21 days before arrival: full night\\u2019s cancellation fee per villa<\\/p><p>\\u2022 No shows and early departures will be charged in full for the total number of nights per room reserved<\\/p>\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-25 03:24:56\"}}', '2026-03-24 19:24:56', '2026-03-24 19:24:56'),
(25, 2, 'Hotel', 'updated', 78, 'App\\Models\\Hotel', '{\"changed\":[\"address\",\"description\",\"additional_info\",\"status\",\"cover\",\"map\",\"latitude\",\"longitude\",\"updated_at\"],\"before\":{\"address\":\"Jl. Tirta Tawar Br.Abangan, Tegallalang, Kecamatan Ubud, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80571\",\"description\":\"Nestled in the heart of Tegallalang, the AnandaDara Ubud Resort &amp; Spa is a testament to the seamless integration of classy design and the natural beauty of Bali. Expertly crafted by acclaimed Balinese architect, Miyoga, the resort is a harmonious blend of traditional Balinese elements and modern comforts. Surrounded by lush rice paddies and meticulously manicured gardens, AnandaDara invites guests to a serene retreat that captures the essence of Bali\\u2019s charm.\",\"additional_info\":\"No check in and no check out on - seclusion day (Nyepi Day)&nbsp;\",\"status\":\"Active\",\"cover\":\"1754979501_AnandaDara-Ubud_Main-Pool-scaled.webp\",\"map\":\"https:\\/\\/goo.gl\\/maps\\/LcVmKj6NW6nenT618\",\"latitude\":null,\"longitude\":null,\"updated_at\":\"2025-09-26T09:32:18.000000Z\"},\"after\":{\"address\":\"Kenderan, Bali, Indonesia\",\"description\":\"Nestled in the heart of Tegallalang, the AnandaDara Ubud Resort &amp;amp; Spa is a testament to the seamless integration of classy design and the natural beauty of Bali. Expertly crafted by acclaimed Balinese architect, Miyoga, the resort is a harmonious blend of traditional Balinese elements and modern comforts. Surrounded by lush rice paddies and meticulously manicured gardens, AnandaDara invites guests to a serene retreat that captures the essence of Bali\\u2019s charm.\",\"additional_info\":\"No check in and no check out on - seclusion day (Nyepi Day)&amp;nbsp;\",\"status\":\"active\",\"cover\":\"hotels\\/covers\\/1754979501_AnandaDara-Ubud_Main-Pool-scaled.webp\",\"map\":\"https:\\/\\/www.google.com\\/maps\\/place\\/AnandaDara+Ubud+Resort+%26+Spa\\/@-8.4678317,115.2669621,17z\\/data=!4m10!3m9!1s0x