uring the tour\\r\\n<\\/li><li data-section-id=\\\"rrcx7j\\\" data-start=\\\"428\\\" data-end=\\\"482\\\">\\r\\nMeals as specified in the itinerary (lunch\\/dinner)\\r\\n<\\/li><li data-section-id=\\\"oj0gg1\\\" data-start=\\\"483\\\" data-end=\\\"531\\\">\\r\\nHotel accommodation (for multi-day packages)\\r\\n<\\/li><li data-section-id=\\\"zyhd8u\\\" data-start=\\\"532\\\" data-end=\\\"604\\\">\\r\\nAirport pick-up and drop-off (<span class=\\\"hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline\\\">Ngurah Rai International Airport<\\/span>)\\r\\n<\\/li><li data-section-id=\\\"2ubw75\\\" data-start=\\\"605\\\" data-end=\\\"640\\\">\\r\\nLocal taxes and service charges\\r\\n<\\/li><li data-section-id=\\\"1u0yx59\\\" data-start=\\\"641\\\" data-end=\\\"679\\\">\\r\\nBasic travel insurance (if stated)<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"day_exclude\":\"<ul><li data-section-id=\\\"1azxo2g\\\" data-start=\\\"707\\\" data-end=\\\"752\\\">International and domestic flight tickets\\r\\n<\\/li><li data-section-id=\\\"ijalq5\\\" data-start=\\\"753\\\" data-end=\\\"809\\\">\\r\\nPersonal expenses (laundry, minibar, shopping, etc.)\\r\\n<\\/li><li data-section-id=\\\"qqdy59\\\" data-start=\\\"810\\\" data-end=\\\"911\\\">\\r\\nOptional activities (e.g. watersports at <span class=\\\"hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline\\\">Tanjung Benoa Beach<\\/span>, ATV, swing, etc.)\\r\\n<\\/li><li data-section-id=\\\"p5fika\\\" data-start=\\\"912\\\" data-end=\\\"952\\\">\\r\\nTips and gratuities for driver\\/guide\\r\\n<\\/li><li data-section-id=\\\"1agnxgb\\\" data-start=\\\"953\\\" data-end=\\\"992\\\">\\r\\nTravel insurance (unless specified)\\r\\n<\\/li><li data-section-id=\\\"1th50nd\\\" data-start=\\\"993\\\" data-end=\\\"1033\\\">\\r\\nMeals not mentioned in the itinerary\\r\\n<\\/li><li data-section-id=\\\"hh3nlf\\\" data-start=\\\"1034\\\" data-end=\\\"1063\\\">\\r\\nVisa fees (if applicable)\\r\\n<\\/li><li data-section-id=\\\"1vw3d2y\\\