(1554, 1, 'Activity', 'created', 31, 'App\\Models\\Activity', '{\"changes\":[{\"field\":\"vendor_id\",\"label\":\"Vendor Id\",\"from\":null,\"to\":\"36\"},{\"field\":\"name\",\"label\":\"Name\",\"from\":null,\"to\":\"Night Safari\"},{\"field\":\"duration_minutes\",\"label\":\"Duration Minutes\",\"from\":null,\"to\":\"120\"},{\"field\":\"benefits\",\"label\":\"Benefits\",\"from\":null,\"to\":null},{\"field\":\"descriptions\",\"label\":\"Descriptions\",\"from\":null,\"to\":\"<div>Satisfy your senses with the unforgettable experience of a nighttime adventure in the wilderness.<\\/div><div>A specially designed caged tram will take you on a journey where you will get to witness and hand-feed animals at a close range!<\\/div><div>See our Fire Show, and enjoy a BBQ dinner, with our unique shows included, you will experience a true natural wildlife encounter.<\\/div>\"},{\"field\":\"adult_contract_rate\",\"label\":\"Adult Contract Rate\",\"from\":null,\"to\":0},{\"field\":\"child_contract_rate\",\"label\":\"Child Contract Rate\",\"from\":null,\"to\":0},{\"field\":\"adult_markup_type\",\"label\":\"Adult Markup Type\",\"from\":null,\"to\":\"fixed\"},{\"field\":\"adult_markup\",\"label\":\"Adult Markup\",\"from\":null,\"to\":0},{\"field\":\"child_markup_type\",\"label\":\"Child Markup Type\",\"from\":null,\"to\":\"fixed\"},{\"field\":\"child_markup\",\"label\":\"Child Markup\",\"from\":null,\"to\":0},{\"field\":\"adult_publish_rate\",\"label\":\"Adult Publish Rate\",\"from\":null,\"to\":0},{\"field\":\"child_publish_rate\",\"label\":\"Child Publish Rate\",\"from\":null,\"to\":0},{\"field\":\"capacity_min\",\"label\":\"Capacity Min\",\"from\":null,\"to\":\"2\"},{\"field\":\"capacity_max\",\"label\":\"Capacity Max\",\"from\":null,\"to\":\"100\"},{\"field\":\"includes\",\"label\":\"Includes\",\"from\":null,\"to\":\"<div><ul><li>Walking Safari<\\/li><li>Welcome Drink<\\/li><li>Night Safari Journey (1x)<\\/li><li>Dinner<\\/li><li>The Rhythm of African<\\/li><li>Fire Dance Show<\\/li><li>Animal Encounter<\\/li><li>Tax included<\\/li><li>Valid after 6 PM<\\/li><\\/ul><\\/div>\"},{\"field\":\"excludes\",\"label\":\"Excludes\",\"from\":null,\"to\":null},{\"field\":\"cancellation_policy\",\"label\":\"Cancellation Policy\",\"from\":null,\"to\":null},{\"field\":\"notes\",\"label\":\"Notes\",\"from\":null,\"to\":\"The activities schedules are subject to change or cancellation due to weather circumstances and on the condition of our animals.\"},{\"field\":\"is_active\",\"label\":\"Is Active\",\"from\":null,\"to\":true},{\"field\":\"gallery_images\",\"label\":\"Gallery Images\",\"from\":null,\"to\":\"[\\\"activities\\\\\\/iYs7xKIDXg7yTFti5cyqMZDYhFZq9mJzNttgWNL7.jpg\\\",\\\"activities\\\\\\/eDk9euPeNP5yxS79PhHUJ6dxd60QShcQ6Tv31rXO.jpg\\\",\\\"activities\\\\\\/QoNxondzkWUYt0jsymod36wTibJ5UxP1GqfjBL3g.jpg\\\"]\"},{\"field\":\"activity_type_id\",\"label\":\"Activity Type Id\",\"from\":null,\"to\":2},{\"field\":\"activity_type\",\"label\":\"Activity Type\",\"from\":null,\"to\":\"Adventure\"},{\"field\":\"contract_price\",\"label\":\"Contract Price\",\"from\":null,\"to\":0},{\"field\":\"created_by\",\"label\":\"Created By\",\"from\":null,\"to\":1},{\"field\":\"updated_by\",\"label\":\"Updated By\",\"from\":null,\"to\":1},{\"field\":\"id\",\"label\":\"Id\",\"from\":null,\"to\":31}]}', '2026-04-13 07:32:48', '2026-04-13 07:32:48'),
(1555, 1, 'Activity', 'created', 32, 'App\\Models\\Activity', '{\"changes\":[{\"field\":\"vendor_id\",\"label\":\"Vendor Id\",\"from\":null,\"to\":\"36\"},{\"field\":\"name\",\"label\":\"Name\",\"from\":null,\"to\":\"Varuna Show\"},{\"field\":\"duration_minutes\",\"label\":\"Duration Minutes\",\"from\":null,\"to\":\"60\"},{\"field\":\"benefits\",\"label\":\"Benefits\",\"from\":null,\"to\":null},{\"field\":\"descriptions\",\"label\":\"Descriptions\",\"from\":null,\"to\":\"<div>Step into the realm of The Varuna Show, Indonesia\\u2019s first underwater theatrical dining experience, set in the mesmerizing backdrop of Bali. Witness a world where the depths of the ocean reveal their secrets, intertwining gastronomy with a journey of fantasy and flavor.<\\/div><div><br><\\/div><div><b>The Legend Beneath The Waves<\\/b><\\/div><div>In Bali\\u2019s enchanting underwater world, The Varuna Show unfolds a captivating story. Follow the extraordinary journey of a young prince, a child of land and sea, discovering his inner strength and royal destiny. Amidst majestic sea creatures and armed with a mystical royal necklace, his adventure beneath the waves is an odyssey like no other.<\\/div><div><br><\\/div><div><b>A Spectacle of Storytelling and Culinary Art<\\/b><\\/div><div>Crafted by the visionary Creative Director Peter Wilson, The Varuna Show is more than just a performance; it\\u2019s an immersive experience. Audiences are not mere spectators but integral parts of this underwater odyssey, where each scene is a mesmerizing fusion of awe-inspiring performances and heartfelt storytelling.<\\/div><div>Are you ready to dive into the heart of Indonesia\\u2019s underwater magic? Book your journey now and be part of The Varuna Show, where each moment is a discovery of fantasy and flavors.<\\/div>\"},{\"field\":\"adult_contract_rate\",\"label\":\"Adult Contract Rate\",\"from\":null,\"to\":1200000},{\"field\":\"child_contract_rate\",\"label\":\"Child Contract Rate\",\"from\":null,\"to\