(97, 31, NULL, '1668672290_4BR Bayugita Residence.webp', '4BR Bayugita Residence', 8, 4, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Bayugita Residence is an architectural exercise in simplicity, combining the simple lines of Balinese tradition with details from colonial Java (Victorian antique baths, Venetian and Dutch colonial beds). Cooling breezes move through the interior. There is a dramatic infinity-edge pool stretching towards rice fields.<ul><li>1 COMO Shambhala Suite (96m2, features private jacuzzi)&nbsp;</li><li>2 Terrace Suites &nbsp;(45m2 and 80m2)&nbsp;</li><li>1 Garden room (45m2)&nbsp;</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, '<ul><li>Daily breakfast for: two guests in rooms and suites,&nbsp;four guests in two bedroom villas and COMO Suite, six guests in three bedroom villas, eight guests in four bedroom residences, ten guests in five bedroom residences</li><li>One time joint wellness appointment during the stay</li><li>Complimentary welcome drink and welcome amenity</li><li>Complimentary local bottled water – replenished daily</li><li>Complimentary in-room coffee and tea making facilities</li><li>Complimentary Wi-Fi in rooms and dedicated public areas of the hotel</li><li>Services of a Personal Assistant</li><li>Complimentary use of the steam room, sauna, gym and three natural spring-fed pools</li><li>Access to selected daily wellbeing activities to support/boost immunity systems, such as: yoga, Pilates, functional fitness and hydrotherapy (as per the weekly schedule of activities).&nbsp;</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, 'Active', '2022-11-15 13:04:50', '2025-05-08 20:23:31'),
(98, 31, NULL, '1668672343_4BR Tirta Ening Residence.webp', '4BR Tirta Ening Residence', 8, 4, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Tirta Ening Residence is dominated by a 91sq metre principal COMO Shambhala suite with an exquisite Japanese water garden featuring a private waterfall. The entire Residence has a Zen feel. The sound of water can be heard throughout. The dining and living rooms cover some 113 square metres. There is a central floating pavilion constructed from batu kuning (yellow rock) and teak wood with an ironwood shingled roof, reminiscent of old Javanese homes. Other highlights include hand-carved doors, stone carvings and Chinese antiques. &nbsp;<ul><li>1 COMO Shambhala Suite (91m2, features Japanese garden with private waterfall)&nbsp;</li><li>3 Terrace Suites (63m2, 65m2 and 68m2)</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, '<ul><li>Daily breakfast for: two guests in rooms and suites,&nbsp;four guests in two bedroom villas and COMO Suite, six guests in three bedroom villas, eight guests in four bedroom residences, ten guests in five bedroom residences</li><li>One time joint wellness appointment during the stay</li><li>Complimentary welcome drink and welcome amenity</li><li>Complimentary local bottled water – replenished daily</li><li>Complimentary in-room coffee and tea making facilities</li><li>Complimentary Wi-Fi in rooms and dedicated public areas of the hotel</li><li>Services of a Personal Assistant</li><li>Complimentary use of the steam room, sauna, gym and three natural spring-fed pools</li><li>Access to selected daily wellbeing activities to support/boost immunity systems, such as: yoga, Pilates, functional fitness and hydrotherapy (as per the weekly schedule of activities).&nbsp;</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, 'Active', '2022-11-15 13:05:43', '2025-05-08 20:23:42'),
(99, 31, NULL, '1668672453_4BR Tejasuara Residence.webp', '4BR Tejasuara Residence', 8, 4, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Tejasuara Residence is a bold, primitive-style residence, inspired by Sumba Island (1200 tonnes of stone imported from this island were used in its construction). Detailing includes tribal cloth furnishing, black bamboo beds and thatch roofing. A fire pit burns beside the infinity pool, which overlooks fields of lemongrass, a spice also endemic to Sumba.&nbsp;<ul><li>1 COMO Shambhala Suite (70m2, features private Jacuzzi, outdoor shower, courtyard and pavilion)&nbsp;</li><li>3 Terrace Suites (60m2 and 83m2)</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, '<ul><li>Daily breakfast for: two guests in rooms and suites,&nbsp;four guests in two bedroom villas and COMO Suite, six guests in three bedroom villas, eight guests in four bedroom residences, ten guests in five bedroom residences</li><li>One time joint wellness appointment during the stay</li><li>Complimentary welcome drink and welcome amenity</li><li>Complimentary local bottled water – replenished daily</li><li>Complimentary in-room coffee and tea making facilities</li><li>Complimentary Wi-Fi in rooms and dedicated public areas of the hotel</li><li>Services of a Personal Assistant</li><li>Complimentary use of the steam room, sauna, gym and three natural spring-fed pools</li><li>Access to selected daily wellbeing activities to support/boost immunity systems, such as: yoga, Pilates, functional fitness and hydrotherapy (as per the weekly schedule of activities).&nbsp;</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, 'Active', '2022-11-15 13:07:33', '2025-05-08 20:24:10'),
(100, 31, NULL, '1668672506_5BR Wanakasa Residence.webp', '5BR Wanakasa Residence', 10, 5, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Wanakasa Residence is set amongst the trees, the pool’s semi-circular edge echoing the bend of the Ayung River that lies 100 metres below. The main living pavilion is supported by huge columns fashioned from the wide trunks of Bingkirai trees. Together with teak floors and the ironwood shingle roofs, literally is like a five-star treehouse. Interiors have a contemporary edge, fashioned from light-speckled tiger bamboo and 150-year-old teak.&nbsp;<ul><li>1 COMO Shambhala Suite (73m2, features private Jacuzzi)&nbsp;</li><li>2 Terrace Suites (58m2 each)&nbsp;</li><li>2 Garden rooms (44m2 each)&nbsp;</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, '<ul><li>Daily breakfast for: two guests in rooms and suites,&nbsp;four guests in two bedroom villas and COMO Suite, six guests in three bedroom villas, eight guests in four bedroom residences, ten guests in five bedroom residences</li><li>One time joint wellness appointment during the stay</li><li>Complimentary welcome drink and welcome amenity</li><li>Complimentary local bottled water – replenished daily</li><li>Complimentary in-room coffee and tea making facilities</li><li>Complimentary Wi-Fi in rooms and dedicated public areas of the hotel</li><li>Services of a Personal Assistant</li><li>Complimentary use of the steam room, sauna, gym and three natural spring-fed pools</li><li>Access to selected daily wellbeing activities to support/boost immunity systems, such as: yoga, Pilates, functional fitness and hydrotherapy (as per the weekly schedule of activities).&nbsp;</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, 'Active', '2022-11-15 13:08:26', '2025-05-08 20:24:27'),
(101, 31, NULL, '1668672549_5BR Umabona Residence.webp', '5BR Umabona Residence', 10, 5, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Umabona Residence boasts COMO Shambhala Estate’s grandest accommodation with the COMO Suite, 2 Terrace suites, a Garden room and study all sharing a pool, living and dining room with a wood-fired pizza oven. The aesthetic is inspired by the Majapahit palaces and their formal pleasure gardens. &nbsp;Interiors include hand carved relief’s, fine antiques and courtly furniture. Views are exceptional, looking towards Mount Batu Karu. &nbsp;<ul><li>1 COMO Suite (308m2, features 2 master suites, a private Jacuzzi, private infinite pool, living room and dining room) &nbsp;</li><li>2 Terrace Suites (60m2 each)&nbsp;</li><li>1 Garden room (32m2)&nbsp;</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, '<ul><li>Daily breakfast for: two guests in rooms and suites,&nbsp;four guests in two bedroom villas and COMO Suite, six guests in three bedroom villas, eight guests in four bedroom residences, ten guests in five bedroom residences</li><li>One time joint wellness appointment during the stay</li><li>Complimentary welcome drink and welcome amenity</li><li>Complimentary local bottled water – replenished daily</li><li>Complimentary in-room coffee and tea making facilities</li><li>Complimentary Wi-Fi in rooms and dedicated public areas of the hotel</li><li>Services of a Personal Assistant</li><li>Complimentary use of the steam room, sauna, gym and three natural spring-fed pools</li><li>Access to selected daily wellbeing activities to support/boost immunity systems, such as: yoga, Pilates, functional fitness and hydrotherapy (as per the weekly schedule of activities).&nbsp;</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, 'Active', '2022-11-15 13:09:09', '2025-05-08 20:24:38'),
