(243, 56, NULL, '1669623732_2BR Pool Villa.webp', '2BR Pool Villa', 4, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Size:&nbsp;400 sqm / 4306 ft&sup2;&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p><strong>Breakfast inclusive rates conditions:</strong></p><ul><li>In-house pouring water, coffee and tea, juice of the day at breakfast.</li><li>All the above rates are for single (1) or double (2) occupancy for a Suite or One-Bedroom Villa or four (4) occupants for a Two-Bedroom Villa. Supplement charges apply for extra person.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li>Breakfast is only available at our All Day Dining restaurant &ndash; KEPUH.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</li></ul><p><strong>SUITE &amp; VILLA RATES STANDARD INCLUSIONS:&nbsp;</strong></p><ul><li>Complimentary daily Kappa Senses&rsquo; instant as per resort&rsquo;s schedule.</li><li>Complimentary shuttle service to a designated area in Ubud town based on the resort&rsquo;s schedule.</li><li>Complimentary Wi-Fi in rooms and throughout the resort.</li><li>Complimentary use of the gym and two resort&rsquo;s swimming pool.</li><li>Complimentary welcome drink.</li><li>Complimentary local bottled water &ndash; replenished daily.</li><li>Complimentary fruit basket &ndash; replenished daily.</li><li>Complimentary in-room coffee and tea making facilities.</li><li>Complimentary access to smart TV services (40 International Chain HD TV Channels, HBO Go, Netflix).&nbsp;</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, 'Active', '2022-11-26 13:22:12', '2024-01-24 01:16:55'),
