(664, 123, NULL, '1756181435_1..webp', 'Superior Room', 2, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<ul><li>Room Size:&nbsp;34 m² / 365 sq ft</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, '<ul><li>International buffet breakfast&nbsp;</li><li>Welcome drink and cold towel on arrival&nbsp;</li><li>Air Conditioning&nbsp;</li><li>Electric safety deposit box&nbsp;</li><li>Tea and coffee making facilities&nbsp;</li><li>Mini bar refrigerator&nbsp;</li><li>Hair dryers&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li>IDD telephone&nbsp;</li><li>80 International TV Channel&nbsp;</li><li>Private Balcony&nbsp;</li><li>Free Wi-Fi in all rooms&nbsp;</li><li>Free usage Gymnasium, sauna and steam at Spa Facilities&nbsp;</li><li>Free usage Gecko’s Kid’s Club<br></li></ul><b>ROOM BENEFIT:</b><br><ul><li>Honeymoon will receive honeymoon benefit upon arrival (honeymoon decoration on the bed, welcome tropical fruit and flower \r\narrangement, glass dome chocolates and bathtub tray for room with bathtub).&nbsp;</li><li>Wedding anniversary will receive benefit on the wedding anniversary date (honeymoon decoration on the bed, glass dome chocolates, \r\nflower arrangement with card set up in the room, bathtub tray for room with bathtub).&nbsp;</li><li>Birthday benefit will receive benefit on the birthday date (chocolate petit cake with candle serve in the room or restaurant, flower \r\narrangement with card set up on the dressing table in the room or restaurant table).&nbsp;</li><li>Wedding certificate should be presented during check in or upon reservation made.</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, 'Draft', '2024-04-14 20:38:44', '2025-09-29 17:13:45'),
