(667, 123, NULL, '1756187695_4..webp', 'Family Room with Bunk Bed', 2, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<ul><li>Room Size:&nbsp;48 m² / 516 sq ft</li><li><span>Room Occupancy: 2 Adults + 2 Children&nbsp;<br><br></span></li></ul>', NULL, NULL, '<ul><li>Welcome drink and cold towel on arrival&nbsp;</li><li>Air Conditioning&nbsp;</li><li>Electric safety deposit box&nbsp;</li><li>Tea and coffee making facilities&nbsp;</li><li>Mini bar refrigerator&nbsp;</li><li>Hair dryers&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li>IDD telephone&nbsp;</li><li>80 International TV Channel&nbsp;</li><li>Private Balcony&nbsp;</li><li>Free Wi-Fi in all rooms&nbsp;</li><li>Free usage Gymnasium, sauna and steam at Spa Facilities&nbsp;</li><li>Free usage Gecko’s Kid’s Club<br></li></ul><b>ROOM BENEFIT:</b><br><ul><li>Honeymoon will receive honeymoon benefit upon arrival (honeymoon decoration on the bed, welcome tropical fruit and flower arrangement, glass dome chocolates and bathtub tray for room with bathtub).&nbsp;</li><li>Wedding anniversary will receive benefit on the wedding anniversary date (honeymoon decoration on the bed, glass dome chocolates, flower arrangement with card set up in the room, bathtub tray for room with bathtub).&nbsp;</li><li>Birthday benefit will receive benefit on the birthday date (chocolate petit cake with candle serve in the room or restaurant, flower arrangement with card set up on the dressing table in the room or restaurant table).&nbsp;</li><li>Wedding certificate should be presented during check in or upon reservation made.</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, 'Draft', '2024-04-14 20:45:35', '2025-09-29 17:13:45'),
(668, 123, NULL, '1756188357_5..jpg', 'Palace Club Room', 2, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<ul><li>Room Size:&nbsp;<span>56 m² / 602 sq ft<br><br></span></li></ul>', NULL, NULL, '<b>PALACE CLUB PRIVILEGES:</b><br><ul><li>Access to Palace Club Lounge open from 6.30 AM – 11 PM&nbsp;</li><li>Private check in and check out at the Palace Club Lounge&nbsp;</li><li>Late check out until 3:00 PM on day of departure&nbsp;</li><li>Welcome drink &amp; cold towel upon check in at Palace Club Lounge&nbsp;</li><li>Welcome fruits &amp; flowers upon arrival&nbsp;</li><li>Complimentary pressing service for 4 (four) garments on arrival day&nbsp;</li><li>Complimentary in room bottled water refreshed daily</li></ul><b>PALACE CLUB LOUNGE:</b><br><ul><li>Breakfast 6.30 AM – 11 AM&nbsp;</li><li>Afternoon Tea 3 PM – 5 PM&nbsp;</li><li>Evening Cocktail with assorted snacks 5.30 PM – 7 PM&nbsp;</li><li>Complimentary nonalcoholic beverages 11 AM – 11 PM&nbsp;</li><li>Computers &amp; printer&nbsp;</li><li>WIFI&nbsp;</li><li>Books collection (mini library) and DVD&nbsp;</li><li>Newspapers &amp; magazines&nbsp;</li><li>Complimentary access to the Sport Centre , Sauna, Steam room, Lap Pool and Jacuzzi&nbsp;</li></ul><b>ROOM BENEFIT:</b><br><ul><li>Honeymoon will receive honeymoon benefit upon arrival (honeymoon decoration on the bed, welcome tropical fruit and flower arrangement, glass dome chocolates and bathtub tray for room with bathtub).&nbsp;</li><li>Wedding anniversary will receive benefit on the wedding anniversary date (honeymoon decoration on the bed, glass dome chocolates, flower arrangement with card set up in the room, bathtub tray for room with bathtub).&nbsp;</li><li>Birthday benefit will receive benefit on the birthday date (chocolate petit cake with candle serve in the room or restaurant, flower arrangement with card set up on the dressing table in the room or restaurant table).&nbsp;</li><li>Wedding certificate should be presented during check in or upon reservation made.</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, 'Draft', '2024-04-14 20:47:41', '2025-09-29 17:13:45'),
