(720, 10, NULL, '1728264149_Classic Family.webp', 'Ayodya Resort - Classic Family', 2, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Room size: 48 sqm&nbsp;', NULL, NULL, '<ul><li>Welcome drink &amp; cold towel provided upon arrival.&nbsp;</li><li>Complimentary 24-hour access to the fitness center.&nbsp;</li><li>Complimentary access to all resort activities, kid’s activities at kid’s club and Balinese cultural activities at Bale Banjar.&nbsp;</li><li>Complimentary internet access available throughout the resort.&nbsp;</li><li>Inter-connecting room are available. Please request for connecting room in advance, subject to availability.</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, 'Active', '2024-10-06 18:22:29', '2025-03-25 18:18:38'),
