(762, 52, NULL, '1734595444_2. Deluxe Family Studio Room.jpeg', 'Deluxe Family Studio Room', 2, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<ul><li>Daily buffet breakfast at Sungai Restaurant for 2 people.</li><li>4 bottled mineral water per room per day.</li><li>Complimentary Wi-Fi access and full access to all hotel facilities: GYM and Fitness centre and two swimming pools.</li><li>Daily Shuttle to Ubud center &ndash; drop and pick-up (based on hotel schedule).</li><li>Complimentary daily activities such as yoga class, cycling tour, morning walks, Balinese dance class, and photo sessions. (based on schedule and terms &amp; conditions applies)</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, 'Active', '2024-12-19 00:04:04', '2024-12-19 00:06:57'),
