(824, 129, NULL, '1743048146_1. Studio Suite.jpeg', 'Studio Suite Ocean View', 2, 1, 'Ocean View', 'King Bed', '76', '<ol><li>Furnished balcony with dining table and day bed&nbsp;</li><li>Cocktail making accessories, including cocktail shaker&nbsp;</li><li>Kevala customised ceramic (tea cup &amp; tea pot)&nbsp;</li><li>English fine china and porcelain by Wedgwood&nbsp;</li><li>Sodashi skincare as in-room amenities&nbsp;</li><li>Pillow menu - selection of 5 pillow types&nbsp;</li><li>Dyson hairdryer&nbsp;</li><li>Nespresso coffee machine and capsules&nbsp;</li><li>Bath menu - a menu with curated bath rituals (additonal fees may be apply)&nbsp;</li></ol>', '<p>配有餐桌與日間床的陽台<br data-start=\"362\" data-end=\"365\">雞尾酒調製用具，包括調酒壺<br data-start=\"378\" data-end=\"381\">Kevala 客製化陶瓷（茶杯與茶壺）<br data-start=\"400\" data-end=\"403\">英國 Wedgwood 精緻瓷器<br data-start=\"419\" data-end=\"422\">Sodashi 護膚品作為客房用品<br data-start=\"439\" data-end=\"442\">枕頭選單 – 提供 5 種枕頭選擇<br data-start=\"459\" data-end=\"462\">Dyson 吹風機<br data-start=\"471\" data-end=\"474\">Nespresso 咖啡機與咖啡膠囊<br data-start=\"492\" data-end=\"495\">沐浴選單 – 提供精心設計的沐浴儀式（可能需額外收費）</p>', '<p>带有用餐桌和日间床的配备阳台<br data-start=\"142\" data-end=\"145\">鸡尾酒调制用具，包括摇酒壶<br data-start=\"158\" data-end=\"161\">Kevala 定制陶瓷（茶杯与茶壶）<br data-start=\"179\" data-end=\"182\">英国 Wedgwood 精致瓷器<br data-start=\"198\" data-end=\"201\">Sodashi 护肤品作为客房用品<br data-start=\"218\" data-end=\"221\">枕头菜单 – 提供 5 种枕头选择<br data-start=\"238\" data-end=\"241\">Dyson 吹风机<br data-start=\"250\" data-end=\"253\">Nespresso 咖啡机及咖啡胶囊<br data-start=\"271\" data-end=\"274\">沐浴菜单 – 提供精心策划的沐浴仪式（可能需额外收费）</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<ul><li>Daily breakfast for up to 2 persons at Taru Restaurant available at any time (24-hour)&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li>A curated selection of local and international snacks, along with a variety of selected alcoholic and non-alcoholic beverages, is provided in our Refreshment Gallery (mini bar). Should guests wish for additional replenishments, they will be available at the prices listed&nbsp;</li><li>Unlimited laundry service&nbsp;</li><li>Regent Experience Agent curates personalized experiences that elevate guest journeys. Acting as a central contact for luxury agents, internal teams, and top-tier guests, they ensure smooth communication and a flawless, unforgettable stay.&nbsp;</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, 'Active', '2025-03-26 20:02:26', '2025-10-29 19:47:09'),
