(449, 'Sanur Beach', 120, 150000, 'fixed', 50000, 200000, 'Denpasar, Bali', 'Denpasar', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Jalan Bypass Ngurah Rai, Sanur Kauh, Denpasar, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/Sanur/@-8.7042307,115.254543,2167m/data=!3m2!1e3!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x2dd241c1ce0912c1:0xf026af7177f0d541!8m2!3d-8.7071782!4d115.2626236!16s%2Fm%2F03wdl19?entry=ttu&g_ep=EgoyMDI2MDMyMy4xIKXMDSoASAFQAw%3D%3D', -8.7042307, 115.2545430, '<p>Sanur Beach is a calm and family-friendly coastal destination known for its gentle waves, golden shoreline, and relaxed atmosphere. Famous for its beautiful sunrise views, it’s perfect for swimming, cycling along the beachfront path, and enjoying a peaceful seaside experience.</p>', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/FjvKlBgX2CiMaQPfOpcaEK4TXKGXCEkoXCChgb4i.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-03-26 00:23:33', '2026-03-26 00:23:33', NULL, 2, 2),
