(451, 'Aling-aling Waterfall', 120, 250000, 'fixed', 50000, 300000, 'Buleleng, Bali', 'Buleleng', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT +8', 'Buleleng, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.1732106,115.1057397', -8.1732106, 115.1057397, '<p>Aling Aling Waterfall is a stunning natural attraction known for its powerful cascades, lush tropical surroundings, and adventurous cliff-jumping spots. Perfect for nature lovers and thrill-seekers, it offers a refreshing escape and a chance to experience Bali’s wild, scenic beauty up close.</p>', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/AWI8oModwQZyj5W7Awx5lrSl36oXWCght9GBTja5.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-03-26 00:30:03', '2026-04-09 04:17:54', NULL, 2, 2),
(452, 'Bali Bird Park', 120, 75000, 'fixed', 75000, 150000, 'Singapadu, Bali', 'Gianyar', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Jalan Piakan I, Singapadu, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.5998105,115.2520236', -8.5998105, 115.2520236, '<p>Bali Bird Park is a vibrant wildlife attraction home to hundreds of exotic bird species from Indonesia and around the world. Set within lush gardens, it offers interactive experiences, educational shows, and close-up encounters, making it perfect for families and nature enthusiasts.</p>', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/2i5k8W3SJqP2d1VPsznGwVQLhsvgPONAYl3kIhle.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/WAnEB76Mdhn5xaIIkfvYdpxd1hzdBNYnUMC2dUPh.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/suJ4vgT2Imo83MRrKpnbOsIkGURoJLLoTXBN7hAG.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/e8wOC84CdcTNxzKB6Co6UvGIZXTzOojfyY5uwCiL.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/db6NruMy4Yzy6UqOWcV6dbJLe1gCaH9eW702rZJR.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/rA9PETWY0D0Fd3zreQDV5fqlY1J7iRRKjIbvwqrW.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/rqeH92zHNT2RSoXrEtluxmO5fx0lemUZINwDSgTj.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-03-26 00:32:21', '2026-04-14 09:54:19', NULL, 2, 2),
(453, 'Bali Safari & Marine Park', 120, 500000, 'fixed', 150000, 650000, 'Medahan, Bali', 'Gianyar', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT +8', 'Profesor Ida Bagus Mantra Bypass, Medahan, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.5821976,115.3446824', -8.5821976, 115.3446824, '<p>Bali Safari &amp; Marine Park is a world-class wildlife and entertainment destination featuring exotic animals, interactive exhibits, and immersive safari experiences. Visitors can enjoy close-up animal encounters, cultural performances, and fun activities for all ages, making it a perfect family-friendly attraction.</p>', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/TB2rQuLze7pIOFlUNJGn134mOHODX4YtIx08vwgG.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-03-26 00:36:50', '2026-04-09 06:36:21', NULL, 2, 7),
(454, 'Banyumala Waterfall', 120, 150000, 'fixed', 50000, 200000, 'Buleleng, Bali', 'Buleleng', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Ridge Way, Buleleng, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/Banyumala+Waterfall/@-8.217182,115.0991062,1085m/data=!3m2!1e3!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x2dd18f9d7a04e875:0x4eccd9e08e4d2397!8m2!3d-8.2171873!4d115.1016811!16s%2Fg%2F11f3jy7mcg?entry=ttu&g_ep=EgoyMDI2MDMyMy4xIKXMDSoASAFQAw%3D%3D', -8.2171820, 115.0991062, '<p>Banyumala Twin Waterfalls is a breathtaking natural attraction hidden in northern Bali, known for its twin cascades, lush jungle surroundings, and serene pool at the base. Ideal for nature lovers and photographers, it offers a peaceful escape and a refreshing experience in Bali’s untouched landscape.</p>', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/WquPvvZCs6nKwrpsCCyfY9w4OJzRqYUhtBAiC6Qr.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-03-26 00:39:44', '2026-03-26 00:39:44', NULL, 2, 2),
(455, 'Bali Zoo', 120, 100000, 'fixed', 50000, 150000, 'Singapadu, Bali', 'Gianyar', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Singapadu, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.5918822,115.2630999', -8.5918822, 115.2630999, '<p>Bali Zoo is a family-friendly wildlife park featuring a wide variety of animals from Indonesia and around the world. With interactive experiences, animal shows, and hands-on encounters, it provides an educational and fun destination for visitors of all ages.</p>', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/7xEwO3XIbqRxneC9cn0327JfMXfhmsPg0TeZLYmc.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-03-26 00:43:49', '2026-04-09 06:36:46', NULL, 2, 7),
