(458, 'Goa Gajah', 120, 50000, 'fixed', 50000, 100000, 'Pejeng, Bali', 'Gianyar', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Raya Teges, Pejeng, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.5228287,115.2875139', -8.5228287, 115.2875139, '<p>Goa Gajah, also known as the “Elephant Cave,” is an ancient archaeological site featuring intricate stone carvings, sacred bathing pools, and a serene temple atmosphere. Steeped in history and spirituality, it offers visitors a glimpse into Bali’s rich cultural and religious heritage.</p>', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/nabrLGyxNW094fZndD9oEGLhivheUIThKdw7Hqwf.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-03-26 00:52:11', '2026-04-09 06:45:39', NULL, 2, 7),
(459, 'Handara Gate', 120, 200000, 'fixed', 100000, 300000, 'Pancasari, Bali', 'Buleleng', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', '2, Pancasari, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.2533721,115.1582023', -8.2533721, 115.1582023, '<p>Handara Gate is an iconic Balinese landmark famous for its grand traditional gate framed by lush greenery and misty mountains. A favorite spot for photography, it offers a striking visual experience and a perfect representation of Bali’s cultural architecture.</p>', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/m8zMC13KFqYSxNoVwxlsBNrBPqEpiZnr6ru7Q1aT.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-03-26 00:54:09', '2026-04-09 06:46:18', NULL, 2, 7),
(460, 'Jatiluwih Rice Terraces', 120, 100000, 'fixed', 50000, 150000, 'Tabanan, Bali', 'Tabanan', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Tabanan, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/Jatiluwih+Rice+Terraces/@-8.3564855,115.0776003,17356m/data=!3m1!1e3!4m6!3m5!1s0x2dd227ab020cd7fb:0x2f0f875ff3e6839a!8m2!3d-8.3700942!4d115.1312269!16s%2Fg%2F11b6dfvgqz?entry=ttu&g_ep=EgoyMDI2MDMyMy4xIKXMDSoASAFQAw%3D%3D', -8.3564855, 115.0776003, '<p>Jatiluwih Rice Terraces is a UNESCO World Heritage site renowned for its expansive green rice paddies and traditional Subak irrigation system. Surrounded by rolling hills and mountains, it offers breathtaking landscapes, cultural insights, and a peaceful escape into Bali’s rural charm.</p>', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/hIfIXW7BHBO2ZGQAjnlidIJxcV5xPxLbC0IVAQLw.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-03-26 00:57:49', '2026-03-26 00:57:49', NULL, 2, 2),
(461, 'Sacred Monkey Forest Sanctuary', 120, 100000, 'fixed', 50000, 150000, 'Ubud, Bali', 'Gianyar', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT +8', 'Jl Nyuh Bringin, Ubud, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.5182564,115.2604568', -8.5182564, 115.2604568, '<p>Sacred Monkey Forest Sanctuary is a lush forest sanctuary home to hundreds of playful long-tailed macaques and ancient temples. Visitors can explore scenic walking paths, observe the monkeys in their natural habitat, and experience the spiritual and cultural charm of Ubud.</p>', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/HnldD7Fcj8RG5EdK8N2BMvBtWqO9h2jrv2LQ0gQx.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-03-26 01:01:57', '2026-04-09 07:02:57', NULL, 2, 7),
(462, 'Munduk Waterfall', 120, 50000, 'fixed', 100000, 150000, 'Buleleng, Bali', 'Buleleng', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT +8', 'Jalan Munduk, Buleleng, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/Air+Terjun+Munduk/@-8.2536996,115.0781611,543m/data=!3m1!1e3!4m14!1m7!3m6!1s0x2dd1860ab3946be1:0xd786b7d9107bf1d3!2sAir+Terjun+Munduk!8m2!3d-8.2541032!4d115.0791492!16s%2Fg%2F11b6_prx07!3m5!1s0x2dd1860ab3946be1:0xd786b7d9107bf1d3!8m2!3d-8.2541032!4d115.0791492!16s%2Fg%2F11b6_prx07?entry=ttu&g_ep=EgoyMDI2MDMyMy4xIKXMDSoASAFQAw%3D%3D', -8.2536996, 115.0781611, '<p>Munduk Waterfall is a serene natural attraction nestled in Bali’s lush highlands, surrounded by tropical forests and coffee plantations. Known for its refreshing cascade and peaceful atmosphere, it offers visitors a perfect spot for nature walks, photography, and a tranquil escape from the crowds.</p>', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/kDLWtuFPuQpA9Mrff44yEglgUxmuvSnSjw3nNplb.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-03-26 01:08:02', '2026-03-26 01:08:02', NULL, 2, 2),
(463, 'Penglipuran Village', 120, 50000, 'fixed', 50000, 100000, 'Sulahan, Bali', 'Bangli', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT +8', 'Sulahan, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.4223363,115.3593227', -8.4223363, 115.3593227, '<p>Penglipuran Village is a traditional Balinese village famed for its well-preserved architecture, bamboo-lined streets, and strong cultural heritage. Visitors can experience authentic local life, explore scenic pathways, and enjoy the village’s tranquil and picturesque atmosphere.</p>', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/es3Hkw9WNnWrflk6eYyH8x4weTrkIuOhODlNtJqi.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-03-26 01:10:52', '2026-04-09 06:57:15', NULL, 2, 7),
(464, 'Hidden Canyon Beji Guwang', 120, 50000, 'fixed', 50000, 100000, 'Guwang, Bali', 'Gianyar', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT +8', 'Jalan Dewi Sitha, Guwang, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.6094426,115.2891890', -8.6094426, 115.2891890, '<p>Beji Guwang Hidden Canyon is a stunning natural attraction featuring narrow limestone gorges, flowing streams, and lush greenery. Ideal for adventure seekers, it offers hiking, canyoning, and a unique opportunity to explore Bali’s hidden geological beauty up close.</p>', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/Ar8XsCpw4cvuIVwp39wtb1gk6zcILGJLIh1aeg9b.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-03-26 01:13:26', '2026-04-09 06:47:11', NULL, 2, 7),
(465, 'Bali Countryside Sidemen', 120, 50000, 'fixed', 50000, 100000, 'Tangkup, Bali', 'Karangasem', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Tangkup, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.4990102,115.4224966', -8.4990102, 115.4224966, '<p>Sidemen Countryside is a scenic rural area known for its emerald rice terraces, traditional villages, and serene mountain views. Perfect for trekking, cycling, and cultural exploration, it offers a peaceful escape into Bali’s authentic and picturesque countryside.</p>', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/CcT4DInohvLm0DdRf0ol4ptpURo3cWAYZVNYVXw1.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-03-26 01:17:25', '2026-04-09 06:34:04', NULL, 2, 7),
(466, 'Tegallalang Rice Terrace', 120, 50000, 'fixed', 50000, 100000, 'Tegallalang, Bali', 'Gianyar', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Tegallalang, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.4335648,115.2792001', -8.4335648, 115.2792001, '<p>Tegalalang Rice Terraces is a famous scenic spot near Ubud, known for its iconic layered rice paddies and traditional Subak irrigation system. Surrounded by lush greenery and tropical landscapes, it offers stunning photo opportunities, cultural insight, and a peaceful connection with Bali’s rural beauty.</p>', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/ovBUjyRAOKl2fOo81PDBQule5sqZSPngd0FgK14o.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-03-26 01:19:33', '2026-04-09 07:01:56', NULL, 2, 7),
(467, 'Tegenungan Waterfall', 120, 50000, 'fixed', 50000, 100000, 'Sukawati, Bali', 'Gianyar', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Jalan Ir. Sutami, Sukawati, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.5752533,115.2904881', -8.5752533, 115.2904881, '<p>Tegenungan Waterfall is a popular natural attraction near Ubud, known for its powerful cascade, lush tropical surroundings, and accessible viewing points. Visitors can enjoy swimming, photography, and a refreshing escape into Bali’s vibrant natural beauty.</p>', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/XpTGhygiRuvLLig64PdLBoKdNhNIYEfjn75eOpDA.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-03-26 01:21:46', '2026-04-09 07:06:41', NULL, 2, 7),
(468, 'Tirta Empul Temple', 120, 100000, 'fixed', 50000, 150000, 'Manukaya, Bali', 'Gianyar', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Manukaya, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.4167370,115.3145235', -8.4167370, 115.3145235, '<p>Tirta Empul Temple is a sacred water temple famous for its holy spring used in purification rituals. Surrounded by serene gardens and traditional architecture, it offers visitors a spiritual and cultural experience, allowing them to witness or participate in Bali’s centuries-old cleansing ceremonies.</p>', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/86ZkHf9CzBiS7sWgENjago8AkdE1gl3i9n4cC74I.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-03-26 01:25:36', '2026-04-09 07:07:55', NULL, 2, 7),
(469, 'Tukad Cepung Waterfall', 120, 50000, 'fixed', 50000, 100000, 'Tembuku, Bali', 'Bangli', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT +8', 'Tembuku, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.4422460,115.3878408', -8.4422460, 115.3878408, '<p>Tukad Cepung Waterfall is a magical waterfall hidden within a cave, where sunlight streams through the cliff above, creating a stunning natural spotlight. Surrounded by lush jungle, it offers a unique and picturesque experience for adventurous visitors and photographers alike.</p>', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/RXUgGj8lLTvugWVqgVT3y17vtiBj5oebUZP5ysaD.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-03-26 01:27:43', '2026-04-09 07:09:31', NULL, 2, 7),
(470, 'Wanagiri Hidden Hill Bali', 120, 100000, 'fixed', 50000, 150000, 'Buleleng, Bali', 'Buleleng', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT +8', 'Buleleng, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/Wanagiri+Hidden+Hill+Bali/@-8.2396548,115.1052125,1085m/data=!3m2!1e3!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x2dd18f4408ba9927:0xd30275eb4513b925!8m2!3d-8.2396601!4d115.1077874!16s%2Fg%2F11f03s_7nx?entry=ttu&g_ep=EgoyMDI2MDMyMy4xIKXMDSoASAFQAw%3D%3D', -8.2396548, 115.1052125, '<p>Wanagiri Hidden Hills is a scenic viewpoint known for its Instagram-worthy swings, bird nests, and panoramic views of lakes and mountains. Set amidst lush greenery, it offers visitors a fun and picturesque spot to capture Bali’s natural beauty and enjoy a peaceful outdoor experience.</p>', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/2HwtnMLy63PoZOApXFl3DrpMvajMVVa4xwEMZnbA.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-03-26 01:30:14', '2026-03-26 01:30:14', NULL, 2, 2),
(471, 'Sekumpul Waterfall', 120, 100000, 'fixed', 50000, 150000, 'Sekumpul, Bali', 'Buleleng', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT +8', 'Sekumpul Waterfall Path, Sekumpul, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.1779792,115.1825138', -8.1779792, 115.1825138, '<p>Sekumpul Waterfall is one of Bali’s most stunning waterfalls, featuring multiple cascades surrounded by lush tropical rainforest. Known for its breathtaking scenery and adventurous trek, it offers a refreshing and immersive experience in Bali’s natural beauty.</p>', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/R706AVwpvcMOrWCXZromO4jPkKU9BZxZMhxELLXj.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-03-26 01:35:44', '2026-04-09 07:03:57', NULL, 2, 7),
(472, 'Waterbom Bali', 120, 450000, 'fixed', 100000, 550000, 'Kuta, Bali', 'Badung', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT +8', 'Jalan Kartika Plaza, Kuta, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.7284147,115.1706069', -8.7284147, 115.1706069, '<p>Waterbom Bali is a premier water park featuring thrilling slides, lazy rivers, and family-friendly attractions. Set amidst tropical gardens, it offers fun and excitement for visitors of all ages, making it a perfect destination for a day of adventure and relaxation.</p>', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/ORAzIv3t2MfbOmUoF4pw41Kfq5iUXj8on9zKxMa8.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-03-26 01:38:24', '2026-04-09 07:12:33', NULL, 2, 7),
(473, 'Tirta Gangga', 60, 100000, 'fixed', 50000, 150000, 'Ababi, Bali', 'Karangasem', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT +8', 'Ababi, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.4120034,115.5874383', -8.4120034, 115.5874383, '<p>Tirta Gangga is a beautiful water palace known for its tiered fountains, ornate stone carvings, and tranquil pools surrounded by lush gardens. Visitors can explore the scenic grounds, enjoy serene walks, and experience a peaceful blend of culture and nature in eastern Bali.</p>', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/L6NqqEuiwJIQXswjgWygBh6msPfNcPHQYN4SBElJ.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/DZkdCZrCxmU7uLG2mJBls5cxrAyqhQtmwstmD3VZ.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/MoG38CvlOmklHYiU8viKcm2lUG40h8XCQhfvYaYd.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/at7BabH2Ozvix3km4cqQq5UX2tPkp96RcKO5ULyo.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-03-26 01:42:40', '2026-04-14 09:53:03', NULL, 2, 2),
(474, 'Taman Ayun Temple', 120, 100000, 'fixed', 50000, 150000, 'Mengwi, Bali', 'Denpasar', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Jalan Markandia, Mengwi, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.5421186,115.1724487', -8.5421186, 115.1724487, '<p>Taman Ayun Temple is a historic royal temple surrounded by picturesque gardens and a traditional Balinese moat. Known for its elegant multi-tiered shrines and serene atmosphere, it offers visitors a peaceful cultural experience and a glimpse into Bali’s architectural heritage.</p>', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/jO9jNLRCXMQCUaOIxXZ3t6LLyngmuFKYFWoxUAEZ.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-03-26 01:47:50', '2026-04-09 07:05:09', NULL, 2, 7),
(510, 'Kelingking Beach', 120, 150000, 'fixed', 50000, 200000, 'Nusa Penida Subdistrict, Bali', 'Klungkung - Nusa Penida', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Jalan Raya Senangka, Nusa Penida Subdistrict, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.7512724,115.4731879', -8.7512724, 115.4731879, '<strong data-start=\"41\" data-end=\"61\">Kelingking Beach</strong> is a stunning cliffside destination in Nusa Penida, famous for its T-Rex-shaped coastline, turquoise waters, and dramatic ocean views. A must-visit spot for breathtaking photos and adventurous hikes down to a secluded white-sand beach.', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/nNO858nGgLqe9Ufcv2GZBBsLVjsjjmwMwvAqKpmW.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/msCCOGqXJrDDqtxh3R6UmbA4YjiJRaXA9a3S7ROw.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/a5yWnPe9VebTphxMfYZTGOnq5OatVogWjGioE9rR.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/999x28RDFcMzyqCh0Duf5tYdc7SwViTvemxFUfWm.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/HuF67y8mbyR8cwipVsOJ2Y9HbhRelmDrJ9mt6rbM.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-04-09 08:04:17', '2026-04-14 09:37:12', NULL, 7, 2),
(511, 'Paluang Clift', 60, 150000, 'fixed', 50000, 200000, 'Nusa Penida Subdistrict, Bali', 'Klungkung - Nusa Penida', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Nusa Penida Subdistrict, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.7536210,115.4771706', -8.7536210, 115.4771706, '<strong data-start=\"41\" data-end=\"58\">Paluang Cliff</strong> is a scenic viewpoint in Nusa Penida offering a unique angle of the iconic T-Rex-shaped Kelingking Beach. Surrounded by rugged cliffs and ocean views, it’s perfect for photography, sunset moments, and a quieter alternative to the main viewpoint.', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/6L837rorQh740CTlwq7AE4I3GqfPqzSZn1iEILFD.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/DKKGrksauLt5FwFHTuLHZpWkcBfzewkox5TDVlGK.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-04-09 08:07:29', '2026-04-14 09:38:07', NULL, 7, 2),
(512, 'Manta Cliff', 60, 150000, 'fixed', 50000, 200000, 'Batukandik, Bali', 'Klungkung - Nusa Penida', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Batukandik, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.7918832,115.5259416', -8.7918832, 115.5259416, '<strong data-start=\"41\" data-end=\"56\">Manta Cliff</strong> is a dramatic coastal viewpoint in Nusa Penida, known for its vast ocean panorama and towering limestone cliffs. A perfect spot to witness manta rays offshore, enjoy peaceful surroundings, and capture breathtaking sunset views away from the crowds.', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/5Kyuusct534gUOow3VoppBVd4J5mDH15pPd7I22h.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-04-09 08:11:57', '2026-04-14 09:37:33', NULL, 7, 2),
(513, 'Angel\'s Billabong', 120, 150000, 'fixed', 50000, 200000, 'Nusa Penida Subdistrict, Bali', 'Klungkung - Nusa Penida', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Jalan Crystal Bay, Nusa Penida Subdistrict, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.7334333,115.4490137', -8.7334333, 115.4490137, '<strong data-start=\"41\" data-end=\"62\">Angel’s Billabong</strong> is a natural infinity pool on Nusa Penida, formed by crystal-clear tidal waters and limestone rocks. Known for its stunning ocean views and unique formations, it offers a serene yet dramatic setting best visited during low tide for a safe and unforgettable experience.', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/FmNQN2siagOBGgAgS1yEgAFC4Y2Cw4rpXCXo46Rt.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/NUQVgeEaxpCVZYfXTn8toVKx5OYhoaqOmovK9STO.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/bIH3V4QKCFOYcZKc3bkoL0rzsmu5XouMvSQGRjGV.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/wTIUuJ9k9ersPfzmSoAUqTYrAoQs0TLfAiSzlePr.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-04-13 06:08:05', '2026-04-14 09:30:54', NULL, 1, 2),
(514, 'Diamond Beach', 90, 150000, 'fixed', 50000, 200000, 'Nusa Penida Subdistrict, Bali', 'Klungkung - Nusa Penida', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Pantai Atuh, Nusa Penida Subdistrict, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.7759123,115.6190014', -8.7759123, 115.6190014, '<strong data-start=\"41\" data-end=\"58\">Diamond Beach</strong> is a breathtaking white-sand beach in Nusa Penida, framed by towering cliffs and iconic rock formations. Accessible via scenic stairs, it offers crystal-clear waters, dramatic views, and a perfect spot for sunrise photography and peaceful seaside moments.', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/7nyadD9HjLr0vBM69yxVdMlxAz0NPD69BVqRzikx.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/1vXg9kalT5NBahRXuXgY7zFwdY6fT2NBiG8t82VG.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/mMeF51AmnXbCtCuFkY2HJZavFvOJQhR92YIbs4bU.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/XfTRP6MxcvI2m6WncEvNph73PBFtUHIx95h6pu6J.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-04-13 06:13:16', '2026-04-14 09:35:56', NULL, 1, 2);
INSERT INTO `tourist_attractions` (`id`, `name`, `ideal_visit_minutes`, `contract_rate_per_pax`, `markup_type`, `markup`, `publish_rate_per_pax`, `location`, `city`, `province`, `country`, `timezone`, `address`, `destination_id`, `google_maps_url`, `latitude`, `longitude`, `description`, `gallery_images`, `is_active`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `deleted_at`, `created_by`, `updated_by`) VALUES
(515, 'Atuh Beach', 90, 150000, 'fixed', 50000, 200000, 'Klungkung - Nusa Penida, Bali', 'Klungkung - Nusa Penida', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Pejukutan', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.7731750,115.6216407', -8.7731750, 115.6216407, '<strong data-start=\"41\" data-end=\"55\">Atuh Beach</strong> is a picturesque bay in Nusa Penida, surrounded by dramatic cliffs and unique rock formations. Known for its calm turquoise waters and stunning sunrise views, it’s an ideal spot for relaxing, swimming, and capturing beautiful coastal scenery.', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/kBTwcvyrdO89sfmXaV50n8xcmNyepI5S01kvoXP5.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/QhzXJce3KgcxdhLxxX5DCXl8io6o4zUfVf8zr31V.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/YQfmfW7cPBqoXccFeR8fGxj7WEj2O50Acuj8RCNZ.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/CiyhlwoqYs6Luk23mJlmsTIvmIHp4VrSTy9fdrRp.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/8tT6J93mJHRC7entVGZFlAaV207vu2ivgjmGxalf.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-04-13 06:21:38', '2026-04-14 09:31:50', NULL, 1, 2),
(516, 'Broken Beach', 60, 150000, 'fixed', 50000, 200000, 'Klungkung - Nusa Penida, Bali', 'Klungkung - Nusa Penida', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Sakti', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.7330589,115.4508591', -8.7330589, 115.4508591, '<strong data-start=\"41\" data-end=\"57\">Broken Beach</strong> is a unique coastal formation in Nusa Penida, featuring a natural rock arch over a turquoise lagoon. Known locally as Pasih Uug, it offers dramatic ocean views and a peaceful atmosphere, making it a perfect spot for sightseeing and photography.', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/VyOiHiTDxmfU0mEhEMG4e5bcW6ozQjCDTHrJZbuS.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/kidYcBkXLJhMM8XcVDZ6RIte6talkv7Mh69ew1A1.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/fb7e8IO5S1VXE06WF5mt2VkLjDOYPAVm5VAV9sgn.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/aFXfMKtx0jja3vvaEBtaXqmeCKfJgn3f8mS88cZN.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/iidbkHAmUM1zsL0MdEAqyrLgWQ97C0JvuTEoDETh.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-04-13 06:24:41', '2026-04-14 09:33:48', NULL, 1, 2),
(517, 'Goa Giri Putri Temple', 60, 150000, 'fixed', 50000, 200000, 'Klungkung - Nusa Penida, Bali', 'Klungkung - Nusa Penida', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Jl. Batu Nunggal-Suana, Suana', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.7089240,115.5860746', -8.7089240, 115.5860746, '<strong data-start=\"41\" data-end=\"66\">Goa Giri Putri Temple</strong> is a sacred cave temple in Nusa Penida, accessed through a narrow entrance that opens into a cavern. Inside, visitors experience a spiritual atmosphere with shrines, prayers, and traditional Balinese rituals, making it a unique cultural and religious destination.', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/6mUrVLK1tjQzpYQGKZFr69Drf2cBEbJaSs3hSVjh.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-04-13 06:29:43', '2026-04-14 09:36:17', NULL, 1, 2),
(518, 'Crystal Bay', 120, 150000, 'fixed', 50000, 200000, 'Nusa Penida Subdistrict, Bali', 'Nusa Penida Subdistrict', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Jalan Crystal Bay, Nusa Penida Subdistrict, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.7151810,115.4590130', -8.7151810, 115.4590130, '<strong data-start=\"41\" data-end=\"56\">Crystal Bay</strong> is a beautiful beach in Nusa Penida, known for its clear waters, vibrant marine life, and stunning sunsets. A popular spot for snorkeling and relaxing, it offers a peaceful atmosphere with palm-lined shores and breathtaking ocean views.', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/9rDE1vQZHYxjixyCJO44hu2hRgVCexVNUFm6GzYe.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/0p2AlTKbfZau0Z9OmXQb7pbypcwp21ZFjZ8MeXEL.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/EBLzm48jPo2KylGIW90ngU4L2qqMuhqUan8raDYw.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/pNdem9TPmdhzsfVD6MEGchNTj2WH9panaZQoE0mk.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-04-13 06:33:06', '2026-04-14 09:35:03', NULL, 1, 2),
(519, 'Atuh King Five', 60, 150000, 'fixed', 50000, 200000, 'Nusa Penida Subdistrict, Bali', 'Klungkung - Nusa Penida', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Pantai Atuh, Nusa Penida Subdistrict, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.7788774,115.6169951', -8.7788774, 115.6169951, '<strong data-start=\"41\" data-end=\"71\">Atuh King Five (Raja Lima)</strong> is a stunning viewpoint in Nusa Penida, showcasing dramatic cliffs and scattered islets resembling a “Thousand Islands” landscape. Famous for sunrise views, it offers breathtaking panoramas, peaceful vibes, and one of the island’s most iconic photo spots.', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/DBwvQm0KeGizhVedkWj3BcxzI20uHVrYSVQAeba6.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-04-13 06:36:58', '2026-04-14 09:32:09', NULL, 1, 2),
(520, 'Tembeling Beach', 120, 150000, 'fixed', 50000, 200000, 'Klungkung - Nusa Penida, Bali', 'Klungkung - Nusa Penida', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Batumadeg', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.7707173,115.4969501', -8.7707173, 115.4969501, '<strong data-start=\"41\" data-end=\"60\">Tembeling Beach</strong> is a hidden gem in Nusa Penida, featuring natural rock pools nestled within a lush forest by the sea. Known for its tranquil atmosphere and scenic coastline, it offers a unique blend of jungle, cliffs, and ocean views—perfect for relaxing and exploring.', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/O799syWMjlhWYdf49szjs2JQGlit6KqcOmlpsSvh.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-04-13 06:46:20', '2026-04-14 09:39:23', NULL, 1, 2),
(521, 'Teletubbies Hill', 60, 150000, 'fixed', 50000, 200000, 'Klungkung - Nusa Penida, Bali', 'Klungkung - Nusa Penida', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Tanglad', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.7853795,115.5722093', -8.7853795, 115.5722093, '<strong data-start=\"41\" data-end=\"61\">Teletubbies Hill</strong> is a scenic landscape in Nusa Penida, known for its rolling green hills resembling a natural carpet. Offering peaceful surroundings and wide-open views, it’s a perfect spot for photography, light trekking, and enjoying Bali’s unique countryside scenery.', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/L5YI16MLRtTyYRJJCb80impjywgOUNkJsyROyMOw.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-04-13 06:50:29', '2026-04-14 09:38:58', NULL, 1, 2),
(522, 'Suwehan Beach', 60, 150000, 'fixed', 50000, 200000, 'Klungkung - Nusa Penida, Bali', 'Klungkung - Nusa Penida', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Tanglad', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.7961288,115.6055689', -8.7961288, 115.6055689, '<strong data-start=\"41\" data-end=\"58\">Suwehan Beach</strong> is a hidden paradise in Nusa Penida, featuring soft white sand, towering cliffs, and a distinctive limestone rock formation. Accessible via steep stairs, it offers crystal-clear waters, peaceful surroundings, and a perfect escape for those seeking untouched natural beauty.', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/Ymws4WtW7fN6hVEL4WgO0Kcm3wzbNy4RIhyZ902V.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-04-13 06:54:39', '2026-04-14 09:38:33', NULL, 1, 2),
(523, 'Banah Cliff', 120, 150000, 'fixed', 50000, 200000, 'Nusa Penida Subdistrict, Bali', 'Klungkung - Nusa Penida', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Batumadeg', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.7677398,115.4866505', -8.7677398, 115.4866505, '<strong data-start=\"41\" data-end=\"56\">Banah Cliff</strong> is a dramatic coastal viewpoint in Nusa Penida, known for its iconic limestone rock formation rising from the ocean. Offering wide panoramic views and stunning sunsets, it’s a perfect spot for photography and enjoying the island’s rugged natural beauty.', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/ojUybqXzvjY3yCpE6sKAGBoQsQdp4MqA8YYWH1CT.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/gpgvS2tkXHBYB739oVj8SacVaRIkpVMB72ZW9FxH.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/k8X11JbqKRV12iCYPHqyD2ihDDHWNJ8Z5Fs9GJv0.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-04-13 06:58:24', '2026-04-14 09:32:38', NULL, 1, 2),
(524, 'Bajra Sandhi Monument', 60, 150000, 'fixed', 50000, 200000, 'Denpasar, Bali', 'Denpasar', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT +8', 'Raya Puputan, Dangin Puri Kelod, Denpasar, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.6720571,115.2338362', -8.6720571, 115.2338362, '<strong data-start=\"41\" data-end=\"66\">Bajra Sandhi Monument</strong> is an iconic landmark in Denpasar, dedicated to the history and struggle of the Balinese people. Featuring detailed dioramas and a viewing tower, it offers cultural insight along with panoramic views of the surrounding Renon area.', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/WLEQ1rBMUQqQ5zFPz96gJUaAFPwThwbRejFujxCV.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/4DzwpfLo1ZmbGNTQLlbsKgMhBX9btkGOzvH5wwJY.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/Eer7M33vOV17ilBtdP1DUobo3CMjxOg9TorLmlGE.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-04-13 07:53:25', '2026-04-14 09:50:55', NULL, 1, 2),
(525, 'Gunung Payung Beach', 120, 150000, 'fixed', 50000, 200000, 'Kuta Selatan, Bali', 'Badung', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Road to Launch Site Bukit Timbis, Kuta Selatan, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.8411719,115.1988387', -8.8411719, 115.1988387, '<strong data-start=\"41\" data-end=\"64\">Gunung Payung Beach</strong> is a hidden beach in South Bali, featuring soft white sand, clear turquoise waters, and towering limestone cliffs. Accessible via a scenic staircase, it offers less crowded atmosphere, perfect for relaxing and enjoying untouched coastal beauty.', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/5RN9MBtCuDPDd6U8NHtb4Q0rk6SHGRdUPLI9V3oV.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/yS4q67dp5SrenVsdJ9NqydUZbbwjD4OcLPnebem9.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/REeKVp5lZnGIa5NCzwiRneiOJNtcVuOutv04JKev.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/0SHyawDqTf80GAbyQ4KJh9G6TyUwmfqLCDmZfNlJ.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-04-13 08:01:54', '2026-04-14 09:50:09', NULL, 1, 2),
(526, 'Mount Batur', 120, 650000, 'fixed', 200000, 850000, 'Kintamani, Bali', 'Bangli', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Jalur Daki Batur, Kintamani, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.2398018,115.3779459', -8.2398018, 115.3779459, '<strong data-start=\"41\" data-end=\"56\">Mount Batur</strong> is an active volcano in Bali, famous for its sunrise trekking experience and panoramic views over Lake Batur. Adventurous hikers are rewarded with breathtaking scenery, cool mountain air, and a memorable journey above the clouds.', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/Aj41xvNjNfp0eF5Ka3ACgtFzdSJDLdnGRsIdhySb.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/FvdrxaGYgf3IkmW9gTyri0nratEFH3NxNqRJSJ7R.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/QgMrEWVYQVlSZH1dhqGuOsiavxIiAWBCuf5mPlH0.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/5FBehWaveiZ3o26f7OLYxNrLUqkMD8p1TTxtqgqJ.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/jYhTHhfVS7VNpzloWkaLxmgrN6lkylrpa7XOZrhM.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/t1bslAWsijQHgIc1Qon9dH6LGnQAnX2HqNX45zYT.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-04-13 08:05:53', '2026-04-14 09:49:28', NULL, 1, 2),
(527, 'Bali Botanical Garden', 120, 150000, 'fixed', 50000, 200000, 'Tabanan, Bali', 'Tabanan', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Jalan Kebun Raya, Tabanan, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.2812201,115.1567173', -8.2812201, 115.1567173, '<strong data-start=\"41\" data-end=\"66\">Bali Botanical Garden</strong> is a vast tropical garden in Bedugul, showcasing diverse plant collections, lush forests, and scenic landscapes. Surrounded by cool mountain air, it’s perfect for relaxing walks, picnics, and exploring Bali’s rich biodiversity.', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/yG2llAczhiRY63mr3sHLNW8PD54k9UvGKrZNdl27.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/6zKzoT4emQIgKGMLWYXN5xfNKvhsTJ0TNIXKq3XN.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/cAvCcz2Ebl3S9dnfduposFuEl419gNSZxQBlivwC.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/PWatuPMldcXUVVr5RgTi2AiWXgGncy2WY6szpvvt.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-04-13 08:08:02', '2026-04-14 09:48:25', NULL, 1, 2),
(528, 'Suluban Beach', 120, 150000, 'fixed', 50000, 200000, 'Badung, Bali', 'Badung', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Pantai Suluban, Pecatu', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.8162312,115.0882834', -8.8162312, 115.0882834, '<strong data-start=\"41\" data-end=\"58\">Suluban Beach</strong> is a unique hidden beach in Uluwatu, accessed through narrow cave passages beneath towering cliffs. Famous for its surf breaks and dramatic scenery, it offers a mystical atmosphere, clear waters, and a favorite spot for surfers and adventurous travelers.', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/M9h1vksxUIE3llCbhgfRjoTPdC1cCpa1oeKCcf9A.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/dQuh1V5JN62bCPv9cKPL5z3hWz9tUd8sLt7AwZXF.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/rfQdwA05oLRswu7ZjJuxUSI7zy7El2zC9K8njySh.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/YLBf51FAhdpPrBnMN7yG5rVPJYxd1qaig6yu7RGQ.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/acHoU3jJckrgNdzAVptGYb70L1EqX7JBdzPsNooa.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-04-13 08:19:10', '2026-04-14 09:47:23', NULL, 1, 2),
(529, 'Leke Leke Waterfall', 120, 350000, 'fixed', 50000, 400000, 'Tabanan, Bali', 'Tabanan', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Kerobokan, Mekarsari, Baturiti', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.3640277,115.1979589', -8.3640277, 115.1979589, '<strong data-start=\"41\" data-end=\"64\">Leke Leke Waterfall</strong> is a hidden gem in Bali, featuring a narrow cascade flowing through lush tropical jungle. Surrounded by serene greenery and a peaceful atmosphere, it’s perfect for nature lovers, photography, and a refreshing escape into Bali’s natural beauty.', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/JOj64u0u0P2uJZHUBPh7aPPBJ3wUKASCoKR7ONDS.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/CDZyR1I5QruuAsoIdnfNexlcRRz7aKOIzg4Nejj0.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/91dKDlF0AlljZjrdpEMocUsrvDAZI9g593Nc3DL7.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-04-13 08:23:22', '2026-04-14 09:46:41', NULL, 1, 2),
(530, 'Campuhan Ridge Walk', 120, 250000, 'fixed', 50000, 300000, 'Ubud, Bali', 'Gianyar', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Bukit Campuhan, Ubud, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.5043303,115.2548325', -8.5043303, 115.2548325, '<strong data-start=\"41\" data-end=\"64\">Campuhan Ridge Walk</strong> is a scenic walking trail in Ubud, offering stunning views of rolling green hills and lush valleys. Perfect for sunrise or sunset strolls, it provides a peaceful escape with fresh air, gentle paths, and beautiful natural surroundings.', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/W4FFYkvv33v2Jz3PdQc7RtASq3NlKNnjuphGaDX6.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/uY0ZMpDTrZZK4lo5aFcDlgtRfwBZFZwntcVoYzqh.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/HKYUo1ldB9E7P3BQRCYb7KQ6spnXE8GGvpiNbE3T.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-04-13 08:29:29', '2026-04-14 09:45:50', NULL, 1, 2),
(531, 'Lempuyang Temple', 60, 250000, 'fixed', 50000, 300000, 'Karangasem, Bali', 'Karangasem', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Desa Purwayu, Tri Buana, Kec. Abang', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.3913637,115.6305644', -8.3913637, 115.6305644, '<strong data-start=\"41\" data-end=\"61\">Lempuyang Temple</strong> is one of Bali’s oldest and most sacred temples, famous for the iconic “Gate of Heaven” with views of Mount Agung. Set high in the mountains, it offers a spiritual atmosphere, scenic surroundings, and a rewarding cultural experience.', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/MtKoJPKiaTg6wsT8uGNYU86KcyIGzGbIPDnNi4j8.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/FP2jCBILDoNVJC2tcZj5nsmI3k1hPh15mKTQEhGk.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/QzIdzPjyzgkTtXGwHFFhhcSzYeRKXdu999Q2Lk1O.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/wkMw5U5RWrTjeYpskcD3sWZ44owF8xpBdmfrKV8g.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-04-13 08:37:50', '2026-04-14 09:44:59', NULL, 1, 2),
(532, 'Sangeh Monkey Forest', 120, 250000, 'fixed', 50000, 300000, 'Badung, Bali', 'Badung', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Jl. Raya Sangeh Jl. Brahmana, Sangeh, Kec. Abiansemal', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.4817995,115.2064669', -8.4817995, 115.2064669, '<strong data-start=\"41\" data-end=\"65\">Sangeh Monkey Forest</strong> is a tranquil forest sanctuary in Bali, home to playful long-tailed monkeys and towering nutmeg trees. Offering a mix of nature and culture, it features a sacred temple and peaceful walking paths surrounded by lush greenery.', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/kdSLTViZJi16UfZAxNl95ZJpSnXrMTct3SrHAD5r.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/rsw7bvrGaH2P5vbPso2ebFHgOKUd9bu6qrZKt0Hp.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/RqdSLUriOTrULcKN1K1kxdTXwdRIh10sDyx2yumS.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-04-13 08:41:46', '2026-04-14 09:44:10', NULL, 1, 2),
(533, 'Gunung Kawi Sebatu Temple', 60, 250000, 'fixed', 50000, 300000, 'Gianyar, Bali', 'Gianyar', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Sebatu, Tegalalang', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.4052212,115.2936065', -8.4052212, 115.2936065, '<strong data-start=\"41\" data-end=\"70\">Gunung Kawi Sebatu Temple</strong> is a serene water temple in Bali, known for its crystal-clear spring pools and lush garden surroundings. Offering a peaceful and spiritual atmosphere, it’s a perfect place to experience traditional Balinese purification rituals and natural beauty.', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/ct5tWGsIbUs5pUHrKU691XA8pRpn64TtSv3JKZZO.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/fc3P9CmCcsCK2Bm2J6wmfB0Kkv8QtoaukHVMulJn.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/MGRvu5APOwrJng3moxHlrspUv2Xm2p3duqHiJn3A.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/pl851zjIFAOJEGe2UiXXOg8SzUZe4TwQQVANuwOI.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/FJB27KyyO7ELLz8Z33gvIFlJxjXCR5zYKe4anlfO.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-04-13 08:50:39', '2026-04-14 09:43:26', NULL, 1, 2),
(534, 'Taman Kemuda Saraswati Temple', 60, 150000, 'fixed', 50000, 200000, 'Ubud, Bali', 'Gianyar', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT', 'Jalan Kajeng, Ubud, Ubud, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.5059379,115.2614897', -8.5059379, 115.2614897, '<strong data-start=\"1\" data-end=\"29\" data-is-only-node=\"\">Taman Sari Kemuda Saraswati Temple</strong> is a peaceful water temple in Bali, featuring sacred spring pools and lush natural surroundings. Known for its calm atmosphere and spiritual ambiance, it offers visitors a serene place for reflection and experiencing traditional Balinese rituals.', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/lojRqH4bCMyAZPtRegde8ko1oAc9tniLmGMuQAxe.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/BMMiaheFXa2Of94AWDpxfAk2hIlIAbVFceZkzX0s.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-04-13 08:56:09', '2026-04-14 09:41:45', NULL, 1, 2),
(535, 'Museum Puri Lukisan', 120, 150000, 'fixed', 50000, 200000, 'Ubud, Bali', 'Gianyar', 'Bali', 'Indonesia', 'GMT +8', 'Jalan Raya Ubud, Ubud, Ubud, Bali, Indonesia', 17, 'https://maps.google.com/?q=-8.5051536,115.2603364', -8.5051536, 115.2603364, '<strong data-start=\"41\" data-end=\"64\">Museum Puri Lukisan</strong> is the oldest art museum in Ubud, showcasing a rich collection of traditional and modern Balinese artworks. Surrounded by beautiful gardens, it offers a cultural journey through Bali’s artistic heritage in a peaceful setting.', '[\"tourist-attractions\\/mmCJoEOmyvAJ0M8p8XKVXxeuLF4Mqi2Zub1DSjTn.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/aL3qlN1MxdFT9sUXJpE3YXItJGoL5ywbZqskiQAm.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/9Q1zm0suWjillcBJtEcjLKxfsDM49j06Vl2mUBJ3.jpg\",\"tourist-attractions\\/q0QsKwAhvFc3JkbbQHgXEeDoWi9cf2N0ENPuDVSf.jpg\"]', 1, '2026-04-13 09:05:17', '2026-04-14 09:41:03', NULL, 1, 2);
